{
  "stem": "214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were even-- but this was because my older sister, her best friend, who was not of a very religious Jewish-- I mean, she was Jewish, but not religious-- and it was a very, what-- what you would call, you know, a very emancipated family.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was a ballet teacher, and she insisted to give ballet lessons to me and to my younger sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we did, you know, and I just loved it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what I'm saying, we were-- we were exposed more to also to secular cultural activities.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother was quite interested for some reason.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, then when you, I mean, you-- you get to be a teenager you read all kinds of literature, Polish literature.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- I did not know where-- how it come-- come about, how it came about, but I was interested in I don't know, you know, a little bit of music, a little bit of theater-- we were going-- Was there a large Yiddish theater in Lodz?",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] You know, there were-- there were Yiddish plays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know, you've probably never heard, but when we first came here after the war, there was an actor who was an excellent actor.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Leo Fuchs-- Leo Fuchs, you remember him?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Him, I think, I saw once in the-- in the Yiddish theatre in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a-- there were the Germans, as I remember also.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was the German actors who were coming to Poland because of-- of Nazis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Granach ?] maybe was somebody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some very famous Jewish actors and-- we would go to see, but those plays already were mostly dealing with what was going on Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but they were presented in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
